snippet.title: Fallen Prince | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Get Fallen Prince on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2531010/Fallen_Prince/

Fallen Prince is an atmospheric combat-focused metroidvania with retro elements. Explore a bleak undead zone, hone your skills and rid the kingdom from your brother's vile sorcery.
Game launched for PC on August 17th, 2023 for $2.99 USD. News on console releases in the future.
